snippet.textDisplay: Recently fell in love with range of audio pitch & high notes Ali sethi possesses. He is such an indpiration. This qawali is beyond phenomenal. Made me realise so much. When I was younger I used to listen US songs and used to think that listening to Pakistani music was supposed to be embarrassing. But now I know that our music & dramas are something to take pride in. Nobody could ace this qawali more than Ali sethi & the respected Abida Parveen. Our music combines spirituality & religion and love in such a way that it takes you to heaven. Forever grateful to coke studio for the rejuvenation of art & music in pakistan.
